00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:56,960
 Yeah, so I would say vibe coding is about

205
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:59,140
 raising the floor for everyone in terms of

206
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:00,260
 what they can do in software.

207
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:03,280
 So the floor rises, everyone can vibe code anything,

208
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,720
 and that's amazing, incredible.

209
00:16:05,040 --> 00:16:07,020
 But then I would say agentic engineering is about

210
00:16:07,020 --> 00:16:09,240
 preserving the quality bar of what existed before

211
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,340
 in professional software.

212
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:13,260
 So you're not allowed to introduce vulnerabilities

213
00:16:13,260 --> 00:16:14,140
 due to vibe coding.

214
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:17,740
 You're still responsible for your software,

