00:16:30,500 --> 00:16:32,140
 They're a bit fallible, a little bit stochastic,

221
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,740
 but they are extremely powerful.

222
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:38,080
 And it's how do you coordinate them to go faster without sacrificing

223
00:16:38,080 --> 00:16:38,880
 your quality bar?

224
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:44,940
 And doing that well and correctly is the realm of agentic engineering.

225
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:49,780
 So I kind of see them as different, like one is about maybe raising the floor

